FIELD.name: Gaussian_ID
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Unique identifier based on the field the component is located in and the index assigned by PyBDSF.

FIELD.name: Source_ID
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Unique identifier based on the field the source is located in and the index assigned by PyBDSF.

FIELD.name: Field_ID
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Field name: RACS_HHMM+/-DD.

FIELD.name: RA
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: J2000 right ascension of the source.

FIELD.name: Dec
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: J2000 declination of the source.

FIELD.name: Dec_corr
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: J2000 declination of the source after declination-dependent offsets applied.

FIELD.name: E_RA
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Uncertainty on right ascension from fitting the source position.

FIELD.name: E_Dec
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Uncertainty on declination from fitting the source position.

FIELD.name: E_Dec_corr
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Uncertainty on corrected declination from fitting.

FIELD.name: Total_flux
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Total flux density of the source.

FIELD.name: E_Total_flux_PyBDSF
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Uncertainty in the total flux density from PyBDSF fitting.

FIELD.name: E_Total_flux
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Quadrature sum of the brightness scale and PyBDSF uncertainties for total flux density.

FIELD.name: Peak_flux
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Peak flux density of the source.

FIELD.name: E_Peak_flux_PyBDSF
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Uncertainty in the peak flux density from PyBDSF fitting.

FIELD.name: E_Peak_flux
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Quadrature sum of the brightness scale and PyBDSF uncertainties for peak flux density.

FIELD.name: Maj_axis
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Size of the major axis of the source.

FIELD.name: Min_axis
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Size of the minor axis of the source.

FIELD.name: PA
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Position angle of the source, east of north.

FIELD.name: E_Maj_axis
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Uncertainty in the source major axis.

FIELD.name: E_Min_axis
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Uncertainty in the source minor axis.

FIELD.name: E_PA
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Uncertainty in the source PA.

FIELD.name: DC_Maj_axis
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Deconvolved source major axis.

FIELD.name: DC_Min_axis
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Deconvolved source minor axis.

FIELD.name: DC_PA
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Deconvolved source PA.

FIELD.name: E_DC_Maj_axis
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Uncertainty in the deconvolved source major axis.

FIELD.name: E_DC_Min_axis
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Uncertainty in the deconvolved source minor axis.

FIELD.name: E_DC_PA
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Uncertainty in the deconvolved source PA.

FIELD.name: Noise
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Local estimate of the root-mean-square noise.

FIELD.name: Tile_l
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Direction cosine l of the source with respect to the field centre.

FIELD.name: Tile_m
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Direction cosine m of the source with respect to the field centre.

FIELD.name: Tile_sep
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Angular separation from the field centre.

FIELD.name: Gal_lon
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Galactic longitude of the source.

FIELD.name: Gal_lat
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Galactic latitude of the source.

FIELD.name: PSF_Maj
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Major axis FWHM of the PSF for the field.

FIELD.name: PSF_Min
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Minor axis FWHM of the PSF for the field.

FIELD.name: PSF_PA
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: PA of the PSF for the field.

FIELD.name: S_Code
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Source structure classification by PyBDSF.

FIELD.name: Flag
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Source type flag. 0 == unresolved, 1 == resolved, 2 == spurious.

FIELD.name: Scan_start_MJD
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Observation start time in MJD of the field.

FIELD.name: Scan_length
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Observation length of the field.

FIELD.name: SBID
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Scheduling block ID of the field.

FIELD.name: E_Flux_scale
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Fractional brightness scale uncertiainty.
